    Class Description
    AdminController
    This is responsible for controlling the admin scene when an admin wants to add and remove users

    This class is responsible for creating an Album Instance which is populated in the albums ArrayList
    AlbumController
    This class controls the album scene
    IndividualAlbumController
    This class takes care of the elements and events performed on the Individual Album fxml page.
    IndividualPhotosController
    This class takes care of the elements and events performed on the Individual Photos fxml page.
    IndividualSearchController
    This class takes care of the elements and events performed on the Individual Search fxml page.
    LoginController
    This class is responsible for controlling the logic scene and allowing users or admin to log ina s
    Photo
    This class is responsible for creating a Photo Instance which can be populated into a user's albums
    PhotoController
    This class takes care of the elements and actions performed on the Photos fxml page.
    Photos
    The Photos class is where the application runs from.
    SearchController
    This is responsible for controlling the search scene for when a user wants to search from their existing albums and photos
    Serialize
    This class handles the serializing aspect of the application and saves all of the users information when the app is closed.
    SlideshowController
    This class takes care of the elements and actions performed on the Slideshow fxml page.
    Tag
    The Tag class is used to store and perform the needed operations for the tags for each picture.
    User
    This class is responsible for creating a User Instance which is populated in the UsersList ArrayList
